cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks to generate realistic deepfakes, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the optimization of the system to generate images that are deemed fake, which involves machine learning (cs.AI) and optimization techniques (cs.LG). The resulting artworks also involve graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) elements.
